/-- **В§10.175  End-to-end SQG + full-range Theorem 3.**

From a `HasAubinLionsExtraction` witness + per-level Galerkin `LВІ`
conservation + velocity witness + smooth initial data + uniform `бёўЛў`
bounds on Galerkin at `s = 1` and every `s > 1`, delivers both a
